{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1714128, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 337163, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "　　“呜呼！楚虽三户能亡秦，岂有堂堂中国空无人！”诗人在诗的最后发出了“岂有堂堂中国空无人”的时代最强音。引用战国时“楚虽三戾，亡秦必楚”的楚车民谣作比，用反诘句表明：汉族人民定有英雄人物能赶走女真统治者收复中原。楚民谣虽仅八字，但深刻说明民心不会死、民力可回天这一道理。陆游虽生活于国力衰微偏安江左的南宋，但基于对民心、民力的正确认识，在述志时他坚信中国有人，定能完成北伐事业，其爱国精神感人至深。", "timestamp": 1621817025, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1714130, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 337163, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "摘自陆游 《金错刀行》", "timestamp": 1621817047, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1714132, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 337163, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "夹带私货：昨晚rng夺冠，这是脑中第一句浮现的诗词。", "timestamp": 1621817079, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1714134, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 337163, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "好！", "timestamp": 1621817093, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1714147, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 337163, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "358团团长吕奉先！", "timestamp": 1621817310, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1716317, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 337163, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "字体好看", "timestamp": 1621843510, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1722343, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 337163, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "#338710\n", "timestamp": 1621928038, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 2778, "w": 1717}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 337163, "reply": 7, "tag": null, "text": "#诗词bot\nDay3\n指路#335877\n", "timestamp": 1621816951, "type": "image", "updated_at": 1621928038, "url": "qa/qaiceqie33p6pcij7o2sme4fnq2obvlr.jpeg", "vote": {}}}